Package base_SOM_Objects.som_geom.geom_utils.geom_objs

Class SOM_GeomSmplDataForEx

java.lang.Object
base_SOM_Objects.som_geom.geom_utils.geom_objs.SOM_GeomSmplDataForEx
public class SOM_GeomSmplDataForEx extends Object
This object will hold a reference to a point and the SOM_GeomObj that the point comes from A single SOM Example will be made up of 2 or more of these : 2 for lines, 3 for planes, (triangle) 4 non-coplanar points for spheres (non-degenerate tet)
